Class BasicCelltoRecordWriter<D>

Object
  BasicCelltoRecordWriter<D>
Type Parameters:

All Implemented Interfaces:
DBRecordWriter<D>
@Beta
public class BasicCelltoRecordWriter<D>
extends Object
implements DBRecordWriter<D>

Takes cell groups and produces a list of database write objects. This writer implementation simply adds all the database items that return from the transformer to a list. Once every cell group to be written has been processed, return the list of database objects.
